cli_content:
Interface Management1 is enabled, line protocol is up
  Hardware is Ethernet, address is 00a1.b2c3.d4e5 (bia 00a1.b2c3.d4e5)
  Description: Management Interface
  Internet address is 192.168.1.10/24
  MTU 1500 bytes, IP MTU 1500 bytes
  Unidirectional traffic, rx: 0, tx: 0
  Last clearing of "show interface" counters never
  5 minute input rate 1000 bits/sec, 2 packets/sec
  5 minute output rate 2000 bits/sec, 3 packets/sec
textfsm_template:
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value STATUS (enabled|disabled)
Value LINE_PROTOCOL (up|down)
Value HARDWARE (\S+)
Value ADDRESS (\S+)
Value DESCRIPTION (.*)
Value IP_ADDRESS (\S+\/\d+)
Value MTU (\d+)
Value IP_MTU (\d+)
Value RX_TRAFFIC (\d+)
Value TX_TRAFFIC (\d+)
Value INPUT_RATE (\d+ bits/sec)
Value INPUT_PACKETS (\d+ packets/sec)
Value OUTPUT_RATE (\d+ bits/sec)
Value OUTPUT_PACKETS (\d+ packets/sec)

Start
  ^Interface\s+${INTERFACE}\s+is\s+${STATUS},\s+line\s+protocol\s+is\s+${LINE_PROTOCOL}\s*$$
  ^\s+Hardware\s+is\s+${HARDWARE},\s+address\s+is\s+${ADDRESS}\s+.*$$
  ^\s+Description:\s+${DESCRIPTION}\s*$$
  ^\s+Internet\s+address\s+is\s+${IP_ADDRESS}\s*$$
  ^\s+MTU\s+${MTU}\s+bytes,\s+IP\s+MTU\s+${IP_MTU}\s+bytes\s*$$
  ^\s+Unidirectional\s+traffic,\s+rx:\s+${RX_TRAFFIC},\s+tx:\s+${TX_TRAFFIC}\s*$$
  ^\s+Last\s+clearing\s+of\s+"show\s+interface"\s+counters\s+never\s*$$
  ^\s+5\s+minute\s+input\s+rate\s+${INPUT_RATE},\s+${INPUT_PACKETS}\s*$$
  ^\s+5\s+minute\s+output\s+rate\s+${OUTPUT_RATE},\s+${OUTPUT_PACKETS}\s*$$ -> Record
